Thought for Today: “That is how authentic power is created — intention by intention, and choice by choice. You cannot wish it, pray it or meditate it into being.” ~ Gary Zukav

As I am starting this second week of 2023, I am taking time to reflect on the past. 
But, most importantly, I am looking to and planning for the future.🤩

It’s my Birthday week! What better time to start fresh? 

Lots of exciting plans and intentions are in the works! And I plan on sharing them all with you. 

So follow along with me here at @DistinctlySouthernStyle on this journey called “2023.” 

Are you one to make resolutions and set goals or intentions for each new year? 
I would love to hear your thoughts on how you start your new year.

I was excited when @VEGAMOUR approached me last fall to try their products and give an honest evaluation. 

Since I am reading and seeing various posts and reviews online, I am curious and open to trying their products and sharing my review with you. 

As we age, it is natural that changes occur to our hair; mine is no exception. 

Thinning and hair fallout are enormous problems for many women. Mid-life aliments and menopause can be common triggers, along with stress, vitamin deficiency, and much more.

So I said yes, I would try the product and discuss my Vegamour - Hair Growth Products Review with my readers.

🤩You can read my full review in today’s BLOG POST  at www.DistinctlySouthernStyle.com

❤️This or That? Long or Short?

What’s your style?

No worries! 
Regarding lounge and sleepwear, @MissElaineSleepwear has a style for every taste!

Spring is just around the corner, so it’s an excellent time to stock up on lighter-weight items. And these seersucker robes are fabulous! The only question is, “ Do you prefer a long or short length?”

The classic long seersucker robe features a beautifully embroidered neckline, 3/4 length sleeves which I love, plus two pockets for holding my odds and ends like my glasses.🤓

The shorter robe offers the same features with short sleeves; of course, it is a short robe. 

Okay,  I must admit that I LOVE them both❣️ They are perfect for my Florida lifestyle! The seersucker fabric is ideal for warm weather. 

💘PS. #misselainesleepwear is a beautiful gift idea! 
Valentine’s Day is just around the corner. Maybe you should treat yourself.
